---
Source:
  - Title: Treasury of Traditional Wisdom
    Page: 100
  - Title: Ecclesiasticus
    Location: XVIII 8
Tags:
  - Sacrifice-Death=Illusion=The Phantom Flux of Life
---
The number of the days of men at the most are a hundred years： as a drop of
water of the sea are they esteemed： and as a pebble of the sand, so are a
few years compared to eternity.
